            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In ho<expan><ex>no</ex><abbr>re</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> domus <lb n="2"/>divin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> deabus <lb n="3"/>Quadrubi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> M<lb break="no" n="4"/>arcianius Avi<lb break="no" n="5"/>tianus <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>iles</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> VIII <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>oto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> m<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>pro salute Ias<expan><ex>s</ex><abbr>ae</abbr></expan> Ti<lb break="no" n="8"/>tiol<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> coniugis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 7 (Ende): Buchstabe S klein und oberhalb der Zeile zwischen A und S eingefügt. (B): CIL 13, 11647: Z. 6 (Ende): MER (mit ME-Ligatur); (o. Autor): Z. 4/5: Avit/ianus; Z. 7: Iassae; Cubaynes: Z. 1: ho(no)r(em); Z. 6: MER; Z. 7: Iassae.</p>
            </div>
